This endpoint ‚Äúdeletes‚Äù an object type by marking it as archived. The deletion process is performed safely and is subject to rate limiting. It returns the type‚Äôs details after it has been archived. Proper error handling is in place for situations such as when the type isn‚Äôt found or the deletion cannot be performed because of permission issues.
